---
---

<section class="problem" id="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-headline" style="text-align:center;">You're Paying for AI You Don't Use</h2>
    <div class="problem-grid">
      <div class="card problem-card">
        <div class="problem-icon">&#128176;</div>
        <h3>Monthly Subscriptions</h3>
        <p>Chatbot platforms charge $99-499/month. Quiet month? You still pay. Busy month? You hit limits and pay overages.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card problem-card">
        <div class="problem-icon">&#128270;</div>
        <h3>Hidden Costs</h3>
        <p>API keys, usage tiers, seat licenses, setup fees. You never know what you'll actually spend until the invoice arrives.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card problem-card">
        <div class="problem-icon">&#128683;</div>
        <h3>Zero Transparency</h3>
        <p>Where does your money go? SaaS billing is a black box. You can't verify what you paid for.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="problem-transition">What if you could see every single cent your AI agent spends — in real-time?</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem {
    background: var(--navy);
  }

  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .problem-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .problem-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .problem-card p {
    color: var(--gray-400);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .problem-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .problem-transition {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--purple-light);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
